51.title: Artyon Celestine

episode of.title: To the Pointe with Kristyn Burtt (TV Series 2017– )

51.plot: Artyon Celestine is one of the talented pros on Season 1 of 'Dancing With the Stars: Juniors.' He's also been seen on 'America's Got Talent,' 'Little Big Shots,' and 'Lip Synch Battler Shorties.'

52.title: Elliana Walmsley

episode of.title: To the Pointe with Kristyn Burtt (TV Series 2017– )

52.plot: Elliana Walmsley is a Season 1 'Dancing With the Stars: Juniors' pro, paired with actor Jason Maybaum and mentor Emma Slater. Dance fans also know her from 'Dance Moms' and as the 2018 title winner of Mini Female Best Dancer at the Dance Awards Las Vegas.

53.title: Laganja Estranja

episode of.title: To the Pointe with Kristyn Burtt (TV Series 2017– )

53.plot: Laganja Estranja is familiar to #RuPaulsDragRace viewers from her Season 6 turn on the show. However, dance fans received a spectacular introduction to her work during The Academy episodes of Season 15 on 'So You Think You Can Dance.' Will she audition for Season 16?

54.title: Michael Dameski

episode of.title: To the Pointe with Kristyn Burtt (TV Series 2017– )

54.plot: Michael Dameski was the runner-up on Season 2 of 'World of Dance.' He recently completed the #WorldofDance Live tour and he's ready to make some big moves in the dance world.

55.title: Bailey Sok

episode of.title: To the Pointe with Kristyn Burtt (TV Series 2017– )

55.plot: Bailey Sok is a member of S-Rank, the division final winners for Upper Team on Season 2 of #WorldOfDance. She's 14 years old and taking the dance world by storm.

56.title: JT Church

episode of.title: To the Pointe with Kristyn Burtt (TV Series 2017– )

56.plot: JT Church won Season 1 of 'Dancing With the Stars: Juniors' with his partner, Sky Brown, and mentor, Alan Bersten. He was also the runner-up in Season 13 with All-Star Robert Roldan on #SYTYCD: The Next Generation.

57.title: Artur Adamski

episode of.title: To the Pointe with Kristyn Burtt (TV Series 2017– )

57.plot: Artur Adamski has been in the 'Dancing With the Stars' troupe for four seasons. He hails from Canada where he competed as a professional ballroom dancer all over the world. He also trains other ballroom couples for major competitions.

imdb.plot outline: Popcorn Talk Network, the online broadcast network that features pop culture discussion, news, interviews and commentary and Dance Network, the digital network dedicated to showcasing all styles and genres of dance, proudly present "To The Pointe with Kristyn Burtt", a show that goes behind the scenes in the commercial dance industry. Kristyn chats with the hottest dancers and choreographers in the TV and film. From hip-hop to ballroom, To The Pointe delivers all of the inside scoop you've been looking for.
